    "In conclusion, to provide more accurate development information through the development support process proposed in this study, it is essential to prevent intent degradation in r 1 and deficiencies in r 2 as outlined in the model in Fig. 4.",
    "Advantage and LimitationThe most significant contribution of this study is the realization of a system that automatically provides information useful for the development and design of a desired service through the simple action of the user verbally expressing their needs.",
    "This brings us significantly closer to enabling rapid development of user-requested services.",
    "Another practical advantage is that, thanks to the VA support, no specialized knowledge is required to convey appropriate needs.",
